<h2>Credential Expiry Reminder</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @volunteer.full_name %>,</p>

<p>Your credential <strong><%= @credential.name %></strong> is expiring in <strong><%= @days %> days</strong> on <%= @credential.expires_at.strftime("%d %b %Y") %>.</p>

<p>Please update your credential to ensure continued compliance.</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= volunteer_profile_url(@volunteer) %>">View your profile</a>
</p>
